fields.title: This Is A Test Poem
fields.body:
Oh code, why must you mock me so,
Lines once smooth, now cease to flow.
The app wont work, it makes me scream,
Errors dance, and kill the dream.

Tables missing, prompts astray,
I debug and curse the day.
But in the end, Ill make it right,
One more push, through sleepless night.
this is a test message because I want to see teh shape of the message bubbles
message test, how does this look
how does this message look now
